body:
I found this image while looking through old MineCraft screenshots of mine that I put on imgur a long time ago, and I'm wondering if anyone could perhaps tell me the name of this map, where I could find it, and if it could perhaps be added to Avicus at some point in the near future.

(As far as I know, this is the only screenshot of the map that I have. I don't remember where or exactly when I saw this; I only saved the screenshot because, at the time, someone posted an IP address for their own MineCraft server, and I wanted to save a pic of it so that I could check it out later. That server probably doesn't exist anymore anyway, so I think having that in the image at the link below shouldn't be a problem.)

http://i.imgur.com/9wuFj1G.png
